description: |-
  The license on the spec itself has not been specified yet. From discussions, this was just an oversight.

  License should be specified (e.g. as LICENSE.txt file) in the GitHub repo and generated web docs.  Matt suggests it will likely be ASLv2 or CC.

  (The Olm spec has been specified and is public domain).
